          <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Trucker Hats</h3>
          <p style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">The trucker hat's foam front and mesh back make it one of the most breathable options for outdoor work and casual wear. Muck Boot and Durango both carry trucker styles with brand patches — a strong option if you're already in their footwear ecosystem. For non-branded truckers, eBay's depth in this category is hard to beat. Search by mesh color and front panel style to narrow results quickly.</p>

          <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--hairline); margin: 2rem 0;">

          <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Baseball Caps</h3>
          <p style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">Structured vs. unstructured is the primary distinction worth understanding before searching. Structured caps hold their shape and are better for a cleaner look; unstructured caps have a more casual, broken-in silhouette. Amazon carries both at competitive price points. For fitted caps, verify the size chart against your head circumference — sizing varies significantly between brands.</p>

          <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--hairline); margin: 2rem 0;">

          <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Snapbacks</h3>
          <p style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">Snapback adjustability makes them a reliable choice when buying as a gift or for a wardrobe where one size needs to work across wearers. eBay has strong vintage snapback inventory if you're looking for older team or brand styles. For current streetwear snapbacks, Amazon's marketplace depth is typically broader than any single brand store.</p>

          <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--hairline); margin: 2rem 0;">

          <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Beanies</h3>
          <p style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">For cold-weather beanies, material matters more than most buyers realize. Acrylic beanies are the most affordable and hold their shape well; merino wool costs more but regulates temperature significantly better in variable conditions. eBay and Amazon both carry strong beanie depth. Search by material type and cuff style to find what you're after efficiently.</p>

